Package gov.va.med.srcalc.db Description

Data mapping between the Domain Model and the ASRC SQL database. All data mapping is performed by the Hibernate Object-Relational Mapper. Various DAOs (Data Access Objects) provide a domain-specific API for loading objects from the database.

Note, however, that the classes in gov.va.med.srcalc.domain define the vast majority of the data mapping via JPA annotations.
